    "MissionGiver": "Red Wind Linehaul",
    "Title": "Red Wind Special Cargo Recovery",
    "TitleKey": "RedWind_RecoverCargo_Super_Title",
    "Description": "RED WIND LINEHAUL\n'YOUR GOODS IN GOOD HANDS'\n----------------------------\n\nWe have a special assignment for only the most competent contractors. One of our haulers who is sadly no longer with us failed to complete their last job. The cargo they were supposed to deliver is sitting stationary in their former ship in the location listed below.\n\nRECOVERY LOCATION\n     \u00b7 <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>\n\nDROP OFF LOCATION\n     \u00b7 Freight elevator at <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address)</EM4>\n\nI\u2019m not going dance around the issue, this is an extremely challenging job. You\u2019ll need to bring a strong team of skilled pilots with you to deal with the outlaws that killed the previous contractor and a <EM4>heavy-duty tractor beam</EM4> to retrieve the client\u2019s cargo. That said, if you take on this contract, we will make it worth your time.\n\nHOW DID WE DO \u2013 Complete our short feedback survey on our Spectrum page for a chance to enter our monthly prize draw.",
    "DescriptionKey": "RedWind_RecoverCargo_Super_Description",
    "DisplayDescription": "RED WIND LINEHAUL\n'YOUR GOODS IN GOOD HANDS'\n----------------------------\n\nWe have a special assignment for only the most competent contractors. One of our haulers who is sadly no longer with us failed to complete their last job. The cargo they were supposed to deliver is sitting stationary in their former ship in the location listed below.\n\nRECOVERY LOCATION\n     \u00b7 <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4>\n\nDROP OFF LOCATION\n     \u00b7 Freight elevator at <EM4>[Destination|Address]</EM4>\n\nI\u2019m not going dance around the issue, this is an extremely challenging job. You\u2019ll need to bring a strong team of skilled pilots with you to deal with the outlaws that killed the previous contractor and a <EM4>heavy-duty tractor beam</EM4> to retrieve the client\u2019s cargo. That said, if you take on this contract, we will make it worth your time.\n\nHOW DID WE DO \u2013 Complete our short feedback survey on our Spectrum page for a chance to enter our monthly prize draw.",
